title: Riding.The.Bullet.2004.LIMITED.DVDSCR.XviD-HCS
description:
Based on Stephen King's novel.

A young man hitchhiking back home to visit his mother is picked up by a 
mysterious stranger. As the ride goes on, the young man uncovers a terrible 
secret about the stranger, and is given a choice by the stranger. A choice that 
can mean life or death.
